periodic F             !Use periodic or non-periodic (Martyna-Tuckermann approach)
funct    0             !0:pwlda, 1:pbe
ekcut    -1d0          ! Kinetic energy cutt off. Negative values will use ABINIT PAW subroutines to calculate ekcut.
